    <item>
      <title>西班牙银行：银行洪水风险高达 200 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/spanish-banks-flood-zone-exposure-is-20-billion-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据西班牙央行称，西班牙银行通过向家庭发放抵押贷款和向当地企业发放贷款，对遭受致命洪水袭击的瓦伦西亚地区的风险敞口约为 200 亿欧元（218 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/spanish-banks-flood-zone-exposure-is-20-billion-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 12:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯胜选或将提振日元，特朗普胜选或将加剧日元跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/yen-is-first-of-many-japanese-assets-set-to-pivot-on-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果卡马拉·哈里斯在美国总统大选中获胜，有可能支撑日本疲软的货币，而如果唐纳德·特朗普获胜，则可能会提振东京股市，并使日元面临进一步下跌的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/yen-is-first-of-many-japanese-assets-set-to-pivot-on-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 00:54:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
